track_notes:
Parking space along south side of A7 at NY 38766 97167. Verge is just wide enough beyond (and not blocking) access to gate. Above Eweless haggis walking across flank of hill was very hard on my ankles. I think a better route would to go up the ridge from sheep shelter to the top of Whin Fell... Depression after that is quite a small drop. After the depression the track I took could not be bettered.

Car to Wisp Hill 62 mins
Wisp Hill to Pikethaw Hill 54 mins
Pikethaw Hill to car 46 mins
track_title: Wisp Hill and Pikethaw Hill together
